Officially sanctioned documentary films with all the action from football's biggest prize.
 
 
 


1/16 An in-depth documentary looking back on the inaugural edition of the World Cup. 

2/16 Looking back on the fifth edition of the World Cup, when West Germany lifted the trophy.

5/16 A look back on the eighth World Cup, which was won by hosts England. 
 
6/16 The 1970 World Cup in Mexico saw Pele make his final appearance on the world stage 
 
7/16 The 1974 World Cup in West Germany saw the Netherlands introduce total football.
